<taxonomicName authorityName="Bate" authorityYear="1972" box="[637,814,295,320]" class="Ostracoda" family="Cyprididae" genus="Pattersoncypris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Podocopida" pageId="4" pageNumber="175" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[637,814,295,320]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="175">Pattersoncypris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, suboval in lateral view, hump barely pronounced. LV overlapping the RV along the anterodorsal and ventral margins, except in the oral region.
</paragraph>
